                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3>Excellence</h3>
                    <p>Delivering high-quality solutions that exceed expectations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                    <p>Building technology that benefits both business and environment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
